Oh yes, when he had it, yes, he was very good. And he - and he - I remember - I remember when I was a girl, he come home from one race one night, he'd been off all weekend at the races - oh yes, yes - and - he came - he - shouted, where's 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Alice{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
