ys you know. Don't you remember when they stopped all that - caning? They'd always got canes. {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Bern{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} and Ern have had many a - thrashing - at school.

