Well - you see such as - as coming back to the hours we do today see. Eight 'til five. And - getting your fortnight's holiday. See, that's how they started with the meetings. Which they do -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15093081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12929532\charrsid15489323 Better conditions?
