\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15093081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12929532\charrsid15489323 
And that was the first time there was any suggestion of you paying your own way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7891655 AB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12929532\charrsid15489323 Oh yes. And - I said I - I was very frightened to - give
 it to her you know, because - were both very funny about it, but her let me board there on the shelf about a three week before he'd pick it up. Which was fourteen shilling. And it was a lot of money for board then. But - Herbert says, leave it there, she
'
ll pick it up when she wants it. You can't do without all your life. You've never had anything. So it's time you had and you've started courting, you want some clothes and I'm going to start you off. Took me out and - rigged me out, yes, beautiful. Mm. Bu
t he was always good to me, ooh he was. Always good to me that lad. Mm.
