No, oh no, her didn't hurt me. But it was a practical joke which - even me mother had to roar with laughter, how I went. Father says, you'll pay for that. Took 'em all night board it up 'til next day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15093081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12929532\charrsid15489323 Until you could get some glass to put in it?
