Yes. Yes. Yes, then - Bert got married there, I got married there. And Ern, we were all married in less than two years. Were older three. And we all had to get married. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15093081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12929532\charrsid15489323 
You've got a tale to tell me haven't you, about when Herbert came home and you were all sitting round the table or something?
