 Herbert but never us. But we would have never got married if we hadn't have done that. Because there was a - Ern's father'd been killed in the war, they'd got a big family and his mother was depending on him and my mother was still depending on me. And y
ou - you couldn't even mention marriage. Wouldn't listen to you. So - we had to do something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15093081 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12929532\charrsid15489323 So you and Herbert got married rather quickly?
