No - Herbert had a very nice wedding. He did, because he'd saved hard and he'd got - som
e money. Had a very nice - wedding, Herbert did. But I didn't. Mine was a registrar - wedding. Just had a little bit of a do at home between ourselves like. And that was it for me. And - Herbert's wife had her baby. And I had mine just after, but theirs d
ied and mine - lived. It was a beautiful baby. Herbert's was. A girl. Nice. And theirs died.
